---
page_title: Colour palette
description: Colour expresses emotion, as well as tone. It places emphasis on certain areas and creates playful associations within a layout. They must be used in a meaningful and intentional way in order to create patterns and visual cues. Our palette is designed to support a wide range of distinct visual styles in order to provide a well-organised brand. We not only value primary colours but also dark and light variants that can be applied to the UI in different ways.

layout: content
index: true
