  p.bx--type-p.u-pb-6 = current_page.data.description
  p.bx--type-p.u-font-bold Visual Differentiation
  p.bx--type-p
    | We use many colours along with a wide variety of iconography in order to make a distinction between similar types of content.

  .content-block
    h2.bx--type-h4.u-text-blue Main grey scale

    p.bx--type-p
      | Our greys can be used on most UI elements but should be limited to:
    ul.e-list
      li background colours
      li text colours
      li border colours
      li svg fill colours

