    p.bx--type-p
      | The extended palette is made out of the colour variations of each colour from the palette, including all shades, tints and tones. These variants come in handy for analytic charts, dashboards, illustrations or components.
    h2.bx--type-h4.u-pt-4 Black and white variants
    p.note
      | From our primary LUCA colours, the different percentages of white (left) and black (right) complete our palette.

